{
  "stem": "935.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They are the living death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They cling and hold and try.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Had malaria, typhus, all those nice illnesses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when they didn't get better, they were thrown out of the revier, and made to walk down the camp street for all the new people to see.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I think it is then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that you make up your mind-- consciously or subconsciously-- not to close your eyes, not to look down, but to see it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Completely, all of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Every ghastly, crazy bit of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because if you don't, you don't stand a chance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You must-- this is when you say, I will never be hungry in here, or cold, or sick, or frightened, or shudder from what is going on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I will see it all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But, I personally-- I saw it like a movie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I'm watching a movie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I'm in it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I'm playing in this movie, but I'm watching it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I must watch it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Hours we stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Hours.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then a young pretty-- I don't know why they're always blonde and blue-eyed and pretty.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they love guns, those little SS guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They came and one of them-- behind me, a mother asked, where the men are.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "When we're going to see the men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was playing, you know, like you have in the Westerners with the gun, all this fancy stuff.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then she said, idiots!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't you know where they are?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Up here!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you think we're burning up there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Coal?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And behind me, this-- I know she was from Vienna, a mother-- who had her husband and a 10-year-old child on the trucks-- fainted.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And next to me, Fritzi, the opera singer said, my mother is up there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And never said another word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She never spoke again.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
